841
00:35:53,310 --> 00:35:54,550
she will have no complaints or regrets.

842
00:35:55,710 --> 00:35:57,220
Alright. I'm done.

843
00:35:57,220 --> 00:35:57,870
Goodbye.

844
00:35:57,870 --> 00:35:59,030
Wait.

845
00:36:00,710 --> 00:36:04,110
But I saw Yi Shui Han
posted the news online

846
00:36:04,110 --> 00:36:05,310
that his autobiography will be published.

847
00:36:05,310 --> 00:36:07,710
Is it all confirmed?

848
00:36:10,470 --> 00:36:11,860
Why did you follow that account?

849
00:36:11,860 --> 00:36:14,470
Can you follow account with quality news?

850
00:36:15,470 --> 00:36:16,700
I don't know anyway.

851
00:36:16,700 --> 00:36:18,950
I only know that
if Chu Li wants me to trust her,

852
00:36:18,950 --> 00:36:20,070
I'll trust her.

853
00:36:21,030 --> 00:36:21,670
But seriously,

854
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:23,470
terminating the contract
with Yuan Yue Publishing House now

855
00:36:23,470 --> 00:36:25,470
is really not a smart move.

856
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:27,310
It'll only rage another storm.

857
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:34,670
My old man has always thought that

858
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:36,150
I'm not as good as you.

859
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:38,380
But on some matters,
I'm really not convinced.

860
00:36:38,790 --> 00:36:39,630
I know.

861
00:36:40,070 --> 00:36:41,900
You're now doing better than me,

862
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:43,390
but I'm still that legendary

863
00:36:43,390 --> 00:36:44,510
kid next door.

864
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:46,300
Then let's call it a match.

865
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:48,940
Trust Chu Li. She'll make sure your book

866
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:50,260
is published according to plan.

867
00:36:50,750 --> 00:36:52,750
When that time comes,
the match will be real.

868
00:36:54,870 --> 00:36:56,830
Alright. Tell Chu Li

869
00:36:57,030 --> 00:36:58,030
I'll wait for her.

870
00:36:59,670 --> 00:37:01,270
Why am I always the messenger?

871
00:37:01,270 --> 00:37:02,590
I'll send voice mail.

872
00:37:05,950 --> 00:37:07,030
I'm leaving. Goodbye.

873
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:07,950
Goodbye.

874
00:37:11,660 --> 00:37:17,200
[Yuan Yue Publishing House]

875
00:37:28,950 --> 00:37:29,630
Director Gu.

876
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:31,110
Any news from Director Lu Fang?

877
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:32,590
The flight delayed.

878
00:37:32,590 --> 00:37:33,550
The Disappearing Amusement Park,

879
00:37:33,550 --> 00:37:35,030
is the photocopy sample ready?

880
00:37:35,950 --> 00:37:38,110
Including the extra volumes that were
specially written for publication.

881
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,910
I've printed them into a booklet.

882
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:42,190
You didn't bring Yun Fei's book?

883
00:37:42,710 --> 00:37:44,910
I'll show him the digital copy.

884
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:48,990
Digital copies may be convenient.

885
00:37:48,990 --> 00:37:50,660
But physical book

886
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:52,190
feels good to hold.

887
00:37:52,830 --> 00:37:54,990
Hope we can succeed today

888
00:37:54,990 --> 00:37:56,190
in persuading Director Lu

889
00:37:56,190 --> 00:37:58,390
to buy the movie rights for
The Disappearing Amusement Park.

890
00:37:58,390 --> 00:38:00,430
Mr Jiang's book can then be published.

891
00:38:01,780 --> 00:38:05,110
Director Lu Fang is
on par with Director Li Yu.

892
00:38:05,110 --> 00:38:07,510
But their working styles are different.

893
00:38:07,750 --> 00:38:08,870
Director Li Yu looks at

894
00:38:08,870 --> 00:38:10,260
the commercial potential of the story.

895
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:12,870
Director Lu just follows his heart.

896
00:38:14,270 --> 00:38:17,670
No wonder his works
continuously received big awards.

897
00:38:17,910 --> 00:38:20,070
But I have confidence in Mr Jiang's book.

898
00:38:20,070 --> 00:38:22,430
If he has a good eye,
he'll definitely want it.

899
00:38:23,430 --> 00:38:25,390
Hopefully we get to meet him.

900
00:38:25,910 --> 00:38:27,550
I begged his manager to set

901
00:38:27,550 --> 00:38:29,510
his transit city here.

902
00:38:29,670 --> 00:38:30,830
But I failed to catch him

903
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:33,230
almost every time.

904
00:38:33,230 --> 00:38:34,110
Why?

905
00:38:34,110 --> 00:38:36,660
You offended him before?
He doesn't want to see you?

906
00:38:36,950 --> 00:38:39,110
Director Lu always changes his plan.

907
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:41,470
It's always given his manager a headache.

908
00:38:45,830 --> 00:38:48,550
Everything will be fine.
We'll give our all today.

909
00:38:48,550 --> 00:38:49,630
To heavens or to hell,

910
00:38:49,630 --> 00:38:51,710
we must catch him today.

911
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:55,670
Miss Bei.

912
00:38:56,230 --> 00:38:57,390
[Director Lu changed his ticket.]

913
00:38:57,750 --> 00:38:59,630
What is the destination?

914
00:38:59,630 --> 00:39:00,910
[Linzhou.]

915
00:39:01,750 --> 00:39:03,180
Alright, I got it.

916
00:39:03,180 --> 00:39:04,710
I'll book bullet train tickets now.

917
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:05,700
We should be able to make it.

918
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:06,260
Alright.

919
00:39:07,330 --> 00:39:10,150
[Bullet Train, Out of Service]

920
00:39:12,830 --> 00:39:13,510
What happened?

921
00:39:14,390 --> 00:39:15,870
Bullet train to Linzhou

922
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:17,700
is temporarily out of service today

923
00:39:17,700 --> 00:39:19,670
because of a typhoon
at one of its station.

924
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:20,510
Why don't we

925
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:21,550
buy a plane ticket

926
00:39:21,550 --> 00:39:23,710
to his final destination city?

927
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:26,350
We'll be in trouble
if the flight kept delaying.

928
00:39:27,110 --> 00:39:28,550
We'll drive there.

929
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:38,750
Chief Director Gu, if you're tired,

930
00:39:38,750 --> 00:39:39,750
I can drive.

931
00:39:39,750 --> 00:39:40,910
I have a driving license.

932
00:39:40,910 --> 00:39:42,070
Thanks for offering.

933
00:39:42,070 --> 00:39:43,750
A driver who has a license
but never been on the road.

934
00:39:43,750 --> 00:39:45,150
I don't want to

935
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,110
risk our lives.

936
00:39:47,990 --> 00:39:49,230
With our current speed,

937
00:39:49,230 --> 00:39:50,990
how long will it take?

938
00:39:50,990 --> 00:39:52,630
Half an hour if it is smooth.

939
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:54,990
Great. We'll be in time.

940
00:39:54,990 --> 00:39:58,310
Looks like the heavens
is watching over Mr Jiang.

941
00:39:59,670 --> 00:40:00,750
What happened?

942
00:40:01,270 --> 00:40:02,430
We have a flat tyre.

943
00:40:02,590 --> 00:40:03,990
What?

944
00:40:18,590 --> 00:40:19,980
What should we do?

945
00:40:19,980 --> 00:40:21,430
Let's call the helpline.

946
00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:22,710
We don't have time for that.

947
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:26,630
Use the spare tyre.

948
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,110
Let me do it. Let me do it.

949
00:40:28,110 --> 00:40:30,110
You use your driving skill.
I'll use my strength.

950
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,790
Don't act tough.

951
00:40:37,790 --> 00:40:39,630
You'll turn into
the guy you're looking for.

952
00:40:39,630 --> 00:40:40,910
Let me do it.

953
00:40:44,790 --> 00:40:46,470
I think we should do it together.

954
00:40:46,470 --> 00:40:47,430
Alright.

955
00:40:56,270 --> 00:40:57,990
Amazing.

956
00:40:59,030 --> 00:41:00,190
We can still make it.

957
00:41:00,190 --> 00:41:02,150
We'll reach in five minutes.

958
00:41:04,220 --> 00:41:06,510
Miss Bei, we'll reach
Linzhou Airport very soon.

959
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:08,270
Where are you?

960
00:41:08,270 --> 00:41:10,150
[We've passed the security checks.]

961
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:11,990
[Why don't we reschedule
the meeting to next month?]

962
00:41:12,830 --> 00:41:15,350
Alright. Have a safe flight.

963
00:41:17,190 --> 00:41:18,950
They've entered the boarding area?

964
00:41:20,310 --> 00:41:21,230
What should we do?

965
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,910
We won't make it
if we don't do this today.

966
00:41:35,350 --> 00:41:36,870
I've waited for Chu Li.

967
00:41:37,070 --> 00:41:38,150
One day.

968
00:41:38,270 --> 00:41:39,420
24 hours.

969
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:41,150
If she asked you to wait for a day,

970
00:41:41,150 --> 00:41:42,270
why can't you wait for a second day?

971
00:41:42,390 --> 00:41:44,670
That idiot is still rushing about for you.

972
00:41:48,390 --> 00:41:49,990
You get her to come back then.

973
00:41:50,540 --> 00:41:51,750
Don't tire herself out.

974
00:41:52,270 --> 00:41:53,590
My heart aches for her too.

975
00:41:55,350 --> 00:41:56,990
Don't you dare.

976
00:42:01,590 --> 00:42:03,110
Mr Jiang Yu Cheng.

977
00:42:03,950 --> 00:42:05,310
Thank you for coming in today.

978
00:42:05,310 --> 00:42:06,990
I know you're here

979
00:42:06,990 --> 00:42:08,830
to talk about the contract termination.

980
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:10,510
We're really sorry

981
00:42:10,510 --> 00:42:12,470
that our plan affected you.

982
00:42:12,470 --> 00:42:14,190
I can understand

983
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,510
your concerns.

984
00:42:15,910 --> 00:42:17,670
Hence I won't make it hard on you

985
00:42:17,940 --> 00:42:19,470
about the contract termination.

986
00:42:20,140 --> 00:42:21,830
Before we terminate our contract,

987
00:42:21,830 --> 00:42:23,270
I want you to meet someone.

988
00:42:23,830 --> 00:42:25,030
Let's not do this.

989
00:42:25,630 --> 00:42:26,990
I've made up my mind.

990
00:42:27,750 --> 00:42:29,700
Chief Editor Yu, Director Lu is here.

991
00:42:30,910 --> 00:42:32,150
Please come in, Director Lu.

992
00:42:33,630 --> 00:42:35,070
I trust you know that

993
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:36,980
this is the famous Director Lu Fang.

994
00:42:38,990 --> 00:42:40,150
Hi, Director Lu Fang.

995
00:42:40,150 --> 00:42:41,110
It's an honour to meet you.

996
00:42:41,110 --> 00:42:42,070
Same here.

997
00:42:42,070 --> 00:42:44,310
We'll leave you two to discuss further.

998
00:42:50,310 --> 00:42:51,110
Please take a seat, Director Lu.

999
00:42:51,110 --> 00:42:52,190
You too.

1000
00:42:55,590 --> 00:42:56,660
Mr Jiang.

1001
00:42:56,660 --> 00:42:58,670
I finally get to meet you in person.

1002
00:43:08,870 --> 00:43:10,510
Why do you suddenly have a cold?

1003
00:43:10,710 --> 00:43:11,990
You didn't come home the whole night.

1004
00:43:15,870 --> 00:43:16,590
Well...

1005
00:43:16,910 --> 00:43:18,190
I was too exhausted last night.

1006
00:43:18,190 --> 00:43:20,030
Thank you for your concern, Mr Zhou Chuan.

1007
00:43:22,750 --> 00:43:23,710
What are you typing?

1008
00:43:23,990 --> 00:43:26,190
An official publication statement

1009
00:43:26,190 --> 00:43:27,830
of The Disappearing Amusement Park

1010
00:43:27,830 --> 00:43:29,270
on our official platform.

1011
00:43:29,830 --> 00:43:31,470
Didn't we confirm that we'll publish

1012
00:43:31,470 --> 00:43:32,390
Yi Shui Han's book first?

1013
00:43:32,390 --> 00:43:34,430
Why are we changing again?

1014
00:43:35,070 --> 00:43:37,870
I'm sorry, Deputy Editor Miao.

1015
00:43:37,990 --> 00:43:39,950
Director Lu Fang has decided
to make a film

1016
00:43:39,950 --> 00:43:41,270
for The Disappearing Amusement Park.

1017
00:43:41,270 --> 00:43:44,150
He just signed the film rights
licensing agreement with Mr Jiang.

1018
00:43:44,150 --> 00:43:46,510
Shooting is estimated
to be within this year.

1019
00:43:46,510 --> 00:43:48,060
Mr Xia has told the upper management

1020
00:43:48,060 --> 00:43:49,430
about this great news.

1021
00:43:49,430 --> 00:43:50,830
The upper management wants

1022
00:43:50,830 --> 00:43:53,310
this book to be published with priority.

1023
00:43:53,310 --> 00:43:55,510
Hence, if it is not yours,

1024
00:43:55,510 --> 00:43:56,950
it's no use fighting.

1025
00:43:57,350 --> 00:43:58,550
Chu Li, do you really think

1026
00:43:58,550 --> 00:44:00,030
I can't do anything about you?

1027
00:44:00,030 --> 00:44:01,950
What do you want to do?

1028
00:44:05,790 --> 00:44:06,540
What happened?

1029
00:44:06,540 --> 00:44:07,830
Why are you standing here?

1030
00:44:10,270 --> 00:44:11,350
I feel so sleepy.

1031
00:44:12,190 --> 00:44:13,460
I'm going to get some coffee.
